## System Architecture

```
                              VVS Data Lakehouse — Lambda Architecture
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │                                                                                     │
  │  ┌──────────┐    WebSocket     ┌───────────┐      Avro       ┌──────────┐          │
  │  │   DNSE   │ ──────────────► │  Producer  │ ─────────────► │  Kafka   │          │
  │  │ Exchange │    (real-time)   │  (Python)  │  (6 topics)    │  (KRaft) │          │
  │  └──────────┘                  └───────────┘  Wire Format    └────┬─────┘          │
  │                                                                    │                │
  │                     ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┤                │
  │                     │                                              │                │
  │    ┌────────────────▼───────────┐                  ┌──────────────▼──────────┐     │
  │    │     SPEED LAYER            │                  │     BATCH LAYER         │     │
  │    │  Spark Structured Streaming│                  │  Spark Batch Jobs       │     │
  │    │  ┌──────────────────────┐  │                  │  ┌───────────────────┐  │     │
  │    │  │ vnstock_stream_to_   │  │                  │  │ vnstock_bronze_   │  │     │
  │    │  │ redis.py             │  │                  │  │ stream.py         │  │     │
  │    │  │ (foreachBatch → Redis)│  │                  │  │ (Kafka → Iceberg) │  │     │
  │    │  └──────────┬───────────┘  │                  │  └────────┬──────────┘  │     │
  │    └─────────────│──────────────┘                  └───────────│─────────────┘     │
  │                  │                                             │                    │
  │                  ▼                                             ▼                    │
  │    ┌─────────────────┐                        ┌────────────────────────────┐       │
  │    │     Redis        │                        │     Apache Iceberg         │       │
  │    │  tick/quote/     │                        │     (on MinIO S3)          │       │
  │    │  secdef/expected │                        │  ┌────────┬────────┐      │       │
  │    └────────┬────────┘                        │  │ Bronze │ Silver │ Gold │       │
  │             │                                  │  │ (raw)  │(dedup) │(agg) │       │
  │             │                                  │  └────────┴────────┴──────┘       │
  │             │                                  └──────────────┬─────────────┘       │
  │             │                                                 │                     │
  │    ┌────────▼────────┐       /api/realtime         ┌─────────▼──────────┐          │
  │    │    FastAPI       │◄──────────────────────────►│      Trino          │          │
  │    │    Backend       │       /api/history          │   (SQL Engine)      │          │
  │    │  + WebSocket     │◄───────────────────────────│  Iceberg Connector  │          │
  │    └────────┬────────┘                             └────────────────────┘          │
  │             │                                                                       │
  │    ┌────────▼────────┐                     ┌──────────────────────────────┐         │
  │    │   React 18       │                     │       Airflow                │         │
  │    │   Lightweight    │                     │  ┌──────────────────────┐   │         │
  │    │   Charts 5       │                     │  │ Bronze Kafka Ingest  │   │         │
  │    │  (TradingView)   │                     │  │ Backfill 1m / 1d    │   │         │
  │    └─────────────────┘                     │  │ Compact Bronze→Silver│   │         │
  │                                             │  │ News Crawler         │   │         │
  │    ┌─────────────────────────────────┐     │  └──────────────────────┘   │         │
  │    │  MONITORING                      │     └──────────────────────────────┘         │
  │    │  Prometheus → Grafana            │                                              │
  │    │  Promtail  → Loki                │                                              │
  │    │  cAdvisor + Node Exporter        │                                              │
  │    └─────────────────────────────────┘                                              │
  │                                                                                     │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Data Flow Summary

| Layer | Component | Vai trò |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| **Ingestion** | DNSE WebSocket → Producer → Kafka | Thu thập real-time 6 topics (OHLC Stock/Derivative/Index, Quote, ExpectedPrice, SecurityDef) |
| **Speed Layer** | Spark Streaming → Redis | Cập nhật giá real-time cho Frontend (< 1s latency) |
| **Batch Layer** | Spark Batch → Iceberg Bronze/Silver/Gold | Lưu trữ raw data vào Iceberg tables trên MinIO |
| **Serving Layer** | FastAPI + Trino + Redis | API phục vụ historical data từ Iceberg, real-time từ Redis |
| **Presentation** | React + Lightweight Charts + WebSocket | TradingView-style charting với hybrid History + Realtime |
| **Orchestration** | Airflow (CeleryExecutor) | Schedule Bronze ingest, backfill, compaction, news crawl |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana + Loki + Promtail | Giám sát toàn bộ pipeline: Kafka lag, RAM, CPU, logs |

---

## Tech Stack

| Category | Technology | Version | Vai trò |
|----------|-----------|---------|---------|
| **Message Broker** | Apache Kafka (KRaft) | 3.5.x | 6-topic message bus, no ZooKeeper |
| **Schema Registry** | Confluent Schema Registry | 7.x | Avro schema management |
| **Stream Processing** | Apache Spark Structured Streaming | 3.5.6 | Real-time ETL (Kafka → Redis, Kafka → Iceberg) |
| **Table Format** | Apache Iceberg | 1.9.2 | ACID transactions trên S3, time-travel, schema evolution |
| **Object Storage** | MinIO | Latest | S3-compatible, lưu trữ Iceberg data + metadata |
| **Query Engine** | Trino | Latest | Distributed SQL trên Iceberg tables |
| **Orchestration** | Apache Airflow (CeleryExecutor) | 2.10.x | DAG scheduling, backfill, compaction |
| **Cache / RT Store** | Redis | 7.2 | Real-time tick/quote/secdef serving |
| **API Backend** | FastAPI + Uvicorn | 0.115+ | REST + WebSocket, 2 workers, GZip |
| **Frontend** | React 18 + Lightweight Charts 5 | 18.3.1 | TradingView-style UI, SMA/EMA indicators |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana + Loki + Promtail | Latest | Metrics + Dashboards + Logs |
| **Serialization** | Apache Avro (Confluent Wire Format) | fastavro 1.9.7 | Binary serialization: `[0x00][4B schema-id][avro]` |
| **IAM** | Keycloak | 23.0.7 | OIDC/SAML identity provider |
| **Secrets** | HashiCorp Vault | 1.15 | KV2 secret store, auto-inject vào containers |
| **Containerization** | Docker Compose v2 | Latest | 40+ services, profiles-based deployment |

