## Monitoring Guide

### Dashboard Panels (20 panels)

Truy cập **Grafana** → Dashboard → **VNStock Data Lakehouse — Overview**

| Section | Panel | Ý nghĩa khi demo |
|---------|-------|-------------------|
| **Host Metrics** | Host RAM Usage | RAM used vs total — đảm bảo < 80% |
| | CPU % Gauge | Current CPU load |
| | RAM % Gauge | Nhanh chóng thấy tải RAM |
| | Disk % Gauge | Đảm bảo disk không đầy |
| | Network I/O | RX/TX bandwidth |
| **Kafka Pipeline** | Consumer Group Lag | **Lag = 0** → Spark đuổi kịp WebSocket ⭐ |
| | Messages/sec per Topic | Throughput 6 topics (peak giờ giao dịch ~500 msg/s) |
| **Container Resources** | Container Memory Top 10 | Phát hiện container ngốn RAM |
| | Container CPU | CPU usage vnstock/kafka/spark/redis/trino |
| **Spark & Serving** | Spark Workers | = 2 → cluster healthy |
| | Spark Active Apps | Streaming jobs đang chạy |
| | Redis Memory | < 50MB cho ~175 mã → rất hiệu quả |
| | Container Count | ~20-40 containers running |
| | Uptime | Host uptime |
| | Trino Active Queries | Số query đang chạy |
| **Logs** | Pipeline Logs (Loki) | Real-time logs Producer, Spark, API, Kafka, Airflow |

### Log Queries (Grafana → Explore → Loki)

```logql
# Xem lỗi Producer
{job="vnstock-producer"} |~ "ERROR|error"

# Xem Spark batch triggers
{job="spark"} |~ "batch|trigger|commit"

# Xem API requests
{job="vnstock-api"} |~ "GET|POST|health"

# Xem tất cả ERROR trong pipeline
{job=~"vnstock-producer|spark|vnstock-api|kafka"} |~ "ERROR"
```

