## Project Structure

```
lakehouse-oss-vuong.ngo/
├── docker-compose.yml             # ~3000 dòng, 40+ services, profile-based
├── .env                           # Environment variables (DNSE_API_KEY, symbols...)
│
├── infra/
│   ├── vnstock/                   # ═══ DNSE WebSocket Producer ═══
│   │   ├── Dockerfile
│   │   ├── producer.py            # Avro serialization → 6 Kafka topics
│   │   └── requirements.txt       # fastavro, websocket-client, confluent-kafka
│   │
│   ├── vnstock-api/               # ═══ FastAPI Backend ═══
│   │   ├── Dockerfile             # Non-root, --limit-max-requests=10000
│   │   ├── requirements.txt
│   │   └── app/
│   │       ├── main.py            # Startup health checks, GZipMiddleware
│   │       ├── config.py          # Environment-based config
│   │       ├── connections.py     # Redis async pool + Trino sync factory
│   │       └── routers/
│   │           ├── history.py     # GET /api/history — Iceberg via Trino
│   │           ├── realtime.py    # GET /api/realtime — Redis (tick/quote/secdef)
│   │           ├── ws.py          # WS /api/ws/stream — Bidirectional protocol
│   │           ├── news.py        # GET /api/news — Redis sorted set
│   │           └── symbols.py     # GET /api/symbols — Config-based
│   │
│   ├── vnstock-frontend/          # ═══ React Frontend ═══
│   │   ├── Dockerfile             # Multi-stage: node:20 → nginx:1.25
│   │   ├── nginx.conf             # Reverse proxy + gzip + WebSocket
│   │   ├── package.json           # react 18, lightweight-charts 5, tailwind 3.4
│   │   └── src/
│   │       ├── App.js             # 3-column: Watchlist | Chart | QuotePanel
│   │       ├── components/
│   │       │   ├── CandlestickChart.js  # TradingView-style, SMA/EMA, hybrid data
│   │       │   ├── QuotePanel.js        # Bid/Ask depth, SecDef (Trần/TC/Sàn)
│   │       │   ├── Watchlist.js         # Symbol list + search + % change
│   │       │   └── NewsTicker.js        # Market news with relative timestamps
│   │       └── services/
│   │           └── api.js         # Bidirectional WS, auto-reconnect
│   │
│   ├── airflow/
│   │   ├── dags/
│   │   │   ├── vnstock_bronze_dag.py      # 6-topic Kafka → Bronze Iceberg
│   │   │   ├── vnstock_backfill_news_dag.py  # Backfill + Compact + News
│   │   │   └── _spark_common.py           # Shared Spark config
│   │   └── processing/spark/jobs/vnstock/
│   │       ├── vnstock_bronze_stream.py   # Kafka Avro → Iceberg Bronze
│   │       ├── vnstock_stream_to_redis.py # Kafka Avro → Redis (Speed Layer)
│   │       ├── vnstock_backfill_1m.py     # vnstock3 → 1m + agg 5m/15m/30m/1h/4h
│   │       ├── vnstock_backfill_1d.py     # vnstock3 TCBS → daily from 2015
│   │       ├── vnstock_compact.py         # Bronze → Silver compaction
│   │       └── vnstock_news_crawler.py    # CafeF/Vietstock/VnEconomy → Redis
│   │
│   ├── schema-registry/schemas/   # 6 Avro schemas (.avsc)
│   │   ├── ohlc_stock.avsc        # {symbol, time, open, high, low, close, volume, resolution}
│   │   ├── ohlc_derivative.avsc
│   │   ├── ohlc_index.avsc
│   │   ├── quote.avsc             # {symbol, bid[10], offer[10], totalBid, totalOffer}
│   │   ├── expected_price.avsc    # {symbol, expectedTradePrice, expectedTradeQuantity}
│   │   └── security_def.avsc      # {symbol, basicPrice, ceilingPrice, floorPrice}
│   │
│   ├── prometheus/config/         # prometheus.yml (15 scrape targets) + alert-rules.yml
│   ├── grafana/config/            # grafana.ini + 5 dashboards (auto-provisioned)
│   ├── loki/config/               # loki-config.yml (TSDB, 7-day retention)
│   └── promtail/config/           # promtail-config.yml (6 job targets)
│
└── README.md                      # This file
```

