## API Reference

| Method | Endpoint | Params | Source | Mô tả |
|--------|----------|--------|--------|-------|
| `GET` | `/api/history` | `symbol`, `interval`, `limit`, `end_time` | Iceberg via Trino | Nến lịch sử (7 timeframes) |
| `GET` | `/api/realtime` | `symbol` (optional) | Redis | Tick real-time (1 hoặc tất cả) |
| `GET` | `/api/realtime/quote` | `symbol` | Redis | Bid/Ask depth (10 levels) |
| `GET` | `/api/realtime/secdef` | `symbol` | Redis | Trần/Sàn/Tham chiếu |
| `GET` | `/api/realtime/expected` | `symbol` | Redis | Giá ATO/ATC dự kiến |
| `GET` | `/api/realtime/summary` | `symbol` | Redis (pipeline) | Tổng hợp tick+quote+secdef+expected |
| `GET` | `/api/news` | `source`, `limit` | Redis sorted set | Tin thị trường |
| `GET` | `/api/symbols` | — | Config | Danh sách mã |
| `WS` | `/api/ws/stream` | `symbol` | Redis (poll 1s) | Bidirectional: subscribe, ping/pong |
| `GET` | `/api/health` | — | Redis + Trino | Health check |

### WebSocket Protocol

```
Server → Client:
  {"type": "tick",  "data": {symbol, time, open, high, low, close, volume}}
  {"type": "quote", "data": {symbol, bid[], offer[], ...}}
  {"type": "ping"}

Client → Server:
  {"type": "subscribe", "symbol": "HPG"}   // đổi mã không cần reconnect
  {"type": "pong"}                          // heartbeat reply
```

---

## Airflow DAGs

| DAG ID | Schedule | Mô tả |
|--------|----------|-------|
| `vnstock_bronze_kafka_stream` | Manual | 6-topic Kafka → Bronze Iceberg + stream-to-Redis |
| `vnstock_backfill_daily` | `0 16 * * 1-5` | vnstock3 TCBS daily → Gold (từ 2015) |
| `vnstock_backfill_1m` | Manual | vnstock3/DNSE 1m → Bronze + aggregate 5m/15m/30m/1h/4h |
| `vnstock_compact_bronze_to_silver` | `0 17 * * 1-5` | Dedup + repartition by symbol |
| `vnstock_news_crawler` | `*/30 8-16 * * 1-5` | CafeF/Vietstock/VnEconomy → Redis |

