### Bước 3: Xác nhận dữ liệu qua Trino SQL

Kết nối Trino CLI và chạy các query kiểm tra:

```bash
docker exec -it trino trino --server localhost:8080 --user admin
```

```sql
-- Kiểm tra 1m data
SELECT symbol, count(*) AS rows, 
       from_unixtime(min(time)/1000) AS earliest,
       from_unixtime(max(time)/1000) AS latest
FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_1m
WHERE symbol IN ('VCB','FPT','HPG','TCB','MSN')
GROUP BY symbol
ORDER BY symbol;

-- Kiểm tra daily data
SELECT symbol, count(*) AS rows,
       from_unixtime(min(time)/1000) AS earliest,
       from_unixtime(max(time)/1000) AS latest
FROM iceberg.gold.vnstock_ohlc_1d
WHERE symbol IN ('VCB','FPT','HPG','TCB','MSN')
GROUP BY symbol
ORDER BY symbol;

-- Kiểm tra aggregated timeframes
SELECT 'bronze.vnstock_ohlc_5m' AS tbl, count(*) FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_5m
UNION ALL
SELECT 'bronze.vnstock_ohlc_15m', count(*) FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_15m
UNION ALL
SELECT 'bronze.vnstock_ohlc_30m', count(*) FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_30m
UNION ALL
SELECT 'bronze.vnstock_ohlc_1h', count(*) FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_1h
UNION ALL
SELECT 'bronze.vnstock_ohlc_4h', count(*) FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_4h;

-- Xem 5 nến gần nhất của VCB (1m) — dùng để demo cho sếp
SELECT from_unixtime(time/1000) AS time_vn, open, high, low, close, volume
FROM iceberg.bronze.vnstock_ohlc_1m
WHERE symbol = 'VCB'
ORDER BY time DESC
LIMIT 5;
```

### Expected Output sau backfill

| Table | Mỗi mã | Tổng 5 mã |
|-------|---------|-----------|
| `bronze.vnstock_ohlc_1m` | ~16,200 rows (90 ngày × 180 nến/ngày) | ~81,000 |
| `bronze.vnstock_ohlc_5m` | ~3,240 | ~16,200 |
| `bronze.vnstock_ohlc_15m` | ~1,080 | ~5,400 |
| `bronze.vnstock_ohlc_30m` | ~540 | ~2,700 |
| `bronze.vnstock_ohlc_1h` | ~270 | ~1,350 |
| `bronze.vnstock_ohlc_4h` | ~68 | ~340 |
| `gold.vnstock_ohlc_1d` | ~2,500 (10 năm) | ~12,500 |

